        <mxCell id="gmbBhOnEvEYA-ofwaeZ0-39" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(39, 37, 30); font-family: pplxSerif, pplxSerif, ui-serif, Georgia, Cambria, &amp;quot;Hiragino Mincho ProN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Yu Mincho&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Songti SC&amp;quot;, SimSun, &amp;quot;Songti TC&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, &amp;quot;Songti TC&amp;quot;, MingLiU_HKSCS, &amp;quot;Songti TC&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, AppleMyungjo, Batang, serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; background-color: color(srgb 0.980392 0.972549 0.960784);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;inspect what is available, what is missing, and what looks unreliable.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
